Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 到底要带我们去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们太脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人的根据地居然就在司令部的地下深处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 不光是大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队自身也脱不了关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 也并不全是坏消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是我的身体？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他说“你不是我的灵魂 所以不能跟你走”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体还在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 我们更接近目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 为什么那个白黑猫会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实这里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 那个豆丁女在里面？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 你快点把短裤穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么 动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}愚者的挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么把那样的家伙也带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后的事情交给拉斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯是大总统金格·布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了各种各样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利曹长是南部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔蔓准尉是北部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普雷达少尉被贬到了西部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍克爱中尉似乎成了大总统专用辅佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是表面上的人质嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这个屋子里只有我们和大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器只有一把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样 也有赢的自信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs60\fad(0,200)}（咳）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咳 咳咳 咳咳咳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前 我们住院的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来看过我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全被你骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“别插手 把军队内部全部都当作是敌人”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该是这么命令你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们对我们来说是非常珍贵的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要知道多余的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在时间到来之前乖乖待着就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 不会对你们怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那个时间到来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我们人柱以外的一般人会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了你不必知道多余的事情 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 什么钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了恢复原来的身体 选择成为军队的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家炼金术师制度本身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计就是为了选出人柱的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果之后还要再被你们利用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不如辞掉国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走狗的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被沾得都是血了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的企图
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会让它失败
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这件事告诉其他的术师们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩叫什么名字来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 温莉·洛克贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利塞布尔出生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们的青梅竹马 对你们来说她和家人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,技术不错的机械铠技师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在拉修巴雷工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时被客人和同伴称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚实的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许对她出手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对周围的人也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说不需要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就舍弃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的话 我们都明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这基础上 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以往一样我们处于你们的监视下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对地 让我们继续恢复身体的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续我们的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不干多余的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古大佐准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会说辞职之类的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 即使成为家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法忍受成为一只败犬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且为了我的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱去军服或者舍弃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在都无法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能问你一个问题吗 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么问题？大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死休斯的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说只问一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个…什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头顶上…剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我点零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别多问了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 真小气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是路边的混混吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 大佐 之后再向你汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸色不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和女性约好的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站着个肌肉胡须不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有哪个男人会有好脸色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍克爱中尉 从洗手间回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受阿姆斯壮少佐的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换岗了一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没逃跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪位说了不论发生什么都不要逃避的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候别和我说还是逃跑比较好哦 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又把机械铠弄坏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 还精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没出什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没被奇怪的人跟踪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为爱德很少打电话过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次居然还关心起我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 你以为我多么地…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接到电话我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真的不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之暂时没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么拚命才会成为被攻击的空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了是古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受你的朋友所托
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是清的语言吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 不会读
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是交给等着这家伙的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰芳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会想之后跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后杀了那个女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会做这种偷偷摸摸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我没有和女人打架的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的信条就是不说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 麟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么有即使让这个国家衰退也要发起内乱的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道外面的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巡逻的人暂时不会过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给你疗伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是伊修瓦尔人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这额头的伤疤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你就是斯卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是参加了歼灭伊修瓦尔的炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 没有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静养一段时间就会好起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自增加患者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,床和沙发被占据了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天开始我在哪里睡才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（再说 家里居然多住两个人…）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰芳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 你必须躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 少主没有和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这里有他的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰芳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是得到了贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们一族就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 得马上回国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个消息告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么沉默？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道少主发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体的状况怎么样 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是拉斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,状态不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:14:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说了吗 这个身体是清的皇子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得到成为皇帝的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己接受了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有趣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的王是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被这个皇子这么问过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王是为了人民而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说 没有人民就没有王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终还不是为了欲望而失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 如果一有空隙就准备侵占我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是虎视眈眈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连怪物也想吞下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类欲望到底有多强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统是人造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:15:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾辈想为我国弱小的人民而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大批的人也这么想着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信任着军队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入了军籍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 这个军队却…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辞去军队的工作如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你的性格 留下也只有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种战斗是错误的 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想违背军令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 去叫替补的国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在伊修瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾辈从战斗中逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队的做法是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么想着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我应该为了纠正这种错误而战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有一天不对扭曲的信念和一直逃避的自己感到可耻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在军队再次成为了战场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾辈怎么能一个人夹着尾巴逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐今后打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和大总统说 我还有野心所以不会辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统自己把自己是人造人的事情告诉了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在暗示 即使打倒我 还有在后面操纵的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被他试了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是很光荣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你这么从容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 在和名叫拉斯多的人造人战斗的时候也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称作“兵器 怪物”的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和真正的怪物战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能够切身感受到自己只是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主自愿接受了贤者之石吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 如果我们阻止他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有必要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是生气自己没能尽到护卫的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主还在那个叫古利德的家伙里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要手臂 现在就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…说要现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我介绍个机械铠技师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽快介绍给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在那之前得积蓄体力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去向诺克斯医生拿饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经可以起来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 是叫张梅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是姚家的看门狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你是张家的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:18:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是我 第17皇女 张梅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到这个国家 就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会交给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法达到目的的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要对别人国家的事情插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我受伤了 别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那句台词 我原封不动还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病人就乖乖躺下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对别人国家的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我管你什么国家的事情 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病人万国共通 都是病人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想再弄乱我的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从医生的家里传出未知的病原体全员死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经有过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是乱得一塌糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有谁来收拾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是家人的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离别的老婆和儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要怎么处理我的东西都是我的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾好了就喝杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能来真是帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说也是这副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好在完全没辙的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 术可以用了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样修复就全部完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那些术师的等级完全不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实上午的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让附近的炼金术师来帮忙修复
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起那些家伙真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自信满满地进入现场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始了却说无法用炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上午
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们在地下的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术师先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩维说的话真的可以相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是没有肉体和精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯粹的能量体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点 要考虑之后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是我和阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的术师也无法使用炼金术了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那个豆丁女和斯卡能够使用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们不同的炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能打听出它的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许不使用贤者之石也能夺回阿尔的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个胡须男对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要去还给中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被迫协助他们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺去了大量伊修瓦尔人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被迫协助参与可能会出现更多牺牲者的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要以死来报一箭之仇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来就像是神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.30,0:23:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没有听说伊修瓦尔的全部事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在那块土地上做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部说出来 马可
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.92,0:23:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁这个右手还没有破坏你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:23:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是无休止的蹂躏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.50,0:24:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大地渗入了鲜红的血
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大气中弥漫着焦肉的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.16,0:24:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊修瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不祥的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.78,0:24:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.65,0:24:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第30话 伊修瓦尔歼灭战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.29,0:24:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使只剩一人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要阐述真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:12.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}心神不定  因为我由于不决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}轻微的颤抖着  control过了还在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:20.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太阳也好  运气（月亮）也罢  完全与我无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:21.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}“只有硬上了吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我这样劝说自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:30.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}情况很糟糕  临阵逃脱又没毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:34.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}虽然前途未卜  也只能靠胆量获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:37.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}压制着冲动  寻找敌我之间的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:40.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}唯一需要的是胜利的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:43.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能尝下胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:47.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或者喝下满腔的苦水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:51.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的  一切都是二择其一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}好想操纵命运的轮盘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:01:00.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}绝好的黄金时间  亲自把握机会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}摆出一副扑克脸  设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:09.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}把敌人引入幻想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:16.14,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}无尽的pressure game  跨越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:20.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了跨越荣耀的borderline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:24.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}How many？  我需要支付多少代价？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:29.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}到底舍不得放弃哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:38.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,250)\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:45.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:48.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}谈话直到日出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:51.28,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}牵手直到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:56.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2\i1}就这样明天后天也一直这样形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:22:01.08,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}寂寞的看着街上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:06.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一个人是无法找到温暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:11.92,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}第一次知道爱原来可以如此坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:17.75,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}那是在与你相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:23.01,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:28.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.33,0:22:33.52,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为一个人无法入睡  也无法做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:39.29,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在不安无法到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:44.55,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}即使是没有星星的夜晚也要继续将其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:47.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}和你在一起的话能到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.05,0:22:50.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}一个人无法走过的道路  如果是两个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:53.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}就可以哼着歌走过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:56.51,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2\i1}只要有你在就很幸福
